üßÆ Analisis Risiko dan Probabilitas
========================================================================================
| Aspek                          | Rinciannya                                          |
| -----------------------------  | --------------------------------------------------- |
| üéØ Win Rate Minimal           | 40‚Äì45% sudah cukup profit dengan R:R = 1:2          |
| üõë Max Drawdown               | Hindari lebih dari 3 loss beruntun ‚Üí kurangi lot    |
| üí° Lot Size Rule              | 0.01 per $100 ‚Üí setiap naik $100 tambah 0.01 lot    |
| üßò‚Äç‚ôÇÔ∏è Disiplin Compounding       | Jika loss, jangan naikan lot sampai balance recover |
