üî∞ Strategi Trading Probability Tinggi untuk Gold

Berikut setup khas institutional trading (Smart Money Concept) yang digunakan hedge fund:
========================================================================================================================
| Setup                         | Konfirmasi Entry                               | TP & SL              | R:R          |
| ----------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------- | -------------------- | ------------ |
| **Break of Structure (BOS)**  | Entry di Fair Value Gap (FVG) setelah BOS      | SL di bawah OB       | 1:2 atau 1:3 |
| **Order Block (OB)**          | Entry di OB valid (mitigasi + liquidity sweep) | SL 10‚Äì20 pips        | 1:2          |
| **Liquidity Sweep + FVG**     | Tunggu likuiditas diambil baru entry           | SL di swing high/low | 1:2          |
| **New York Session Reversal** | Entry setelah news fake move                   | SL kecil di spike    | 1:2‚Äì1:4      |
========================================================================================================================

üß≠ Kesimpulan

‚úÖ Target realistis: dari $10 ‚Üí $1,000 bisa dicapai dalam 25‚Äì30 win trade (x2 reward, 10% risk).
‚úÖ Kunci utama: risk management dan konsistensi entry setup (gunakan 1 strategi SMC saja).
‚úÖ Gunakan broker leverage tinggi (1:500), spread kecil (Gold ECN).
‚úÖ Jangan serakah ‚Äî compound itu seni, bukan sprint.
